      "title": "Legal action against those occupying government buildings",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe has said that it is illegal to forcefully occupy the President's Secretariat and the Prime Minister's Office under the guise of people's protest.",
        "He said this after participating in worship at Hunupitiya Gangarama Vihara, Colombo yesterday (20). (a)"
      ],
